<Report ScriptLanguage="CSharp" TextQuality="Regular" ReportInfo.Description="This report demonstrates different QR-Code and Aztec types developed in FastReport Designer: Text, vCard, URI, GEolocation, E-Mail address, E-Mail message, SMS, Call, Event, Wi-Fi, Swiss QR. You can create it with a double-click on BarcodeObject (Barcode Type should be set to &quot;QR Code or Aztec&quot;).&#13;&#10;Additionally, the report shows various decorative QR-Code module shapes (Rectangle, Circle, Diamond, RoundedSquare, PillHorizontal, PillVertical, Plus, Hexagon, Star, Snowflake) with different UseThinModules and Angle settings.&#13;&#10;" ReportInfo.Created="02/21/2008 20:44:59" ReportInfo.Modified="03/19/2026 19:38:41" ReportInfo.CreatorVersion="1.0.0.0">
